AB  - In order to solve forest ecological functions evaluation by hand and independent, decentralized, cumbersome analysis and evaluation methods, based on database technology, GIS component technology, WEBGIS technology, system integration technology theory and methods, this paper gives a seamless integrative system based MIS and GIS in the core of WEBGIS technology and the networking,at the same time ASP.NET C# and the ARCIMS technology are the main methods in the system and SQL SERVER and GEODATABASE is the backstage database. the system can achieve data import/export, data loading, data validation, data analysis and processing, data query, trend forecasting, spatial data automatic acquisition, variation modeling, spatial interpolation, grade distribution established, overlay analysis, partial correlation analysis, time series analysis, evaluation report generation, printouts and other functions and it also can provide comprehensive evaluation and the release of information of forest ecological functions.
